		<item>
		<title>VEE #048 – Mr. Taylor, Part I</title>
		<link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/vocespodcast/~3/5M7glyjMvdE/</link>
		<comments>http://spanish-podcast.com/2009/06/05/mister-taylor-augusto-monterroso/#comments</comments>
