		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://spanish-podcast.com/2008/02/17/vee-018-el-corrido-de-dante/</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[Interview with Eduardo González Viaña, author of El corrido de Dante. Eduardo is from Peru and in this podcast he talks about the inspiration of this book and the current situation of some Hispanic immigrants in the United States.
]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Interview with Eduardo González Viaña, author of <em><strong>El corrido de Dante</strong></em>. Eduardo is from Peru and in this podcast he talks about the inspiration of this book and the current situation of some Hispanic immigrants in the United States.</p>
<div class="feedflare">
