			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>In Part 2 of the <a href="http://www.ritmolatino.org/"><strong>Ritmo Latino</strong></a> interview, Neil Hohmann gives his opinion about crossover musicians (groups that start their careers in Spanish and then &#8220;cross over&#8221; to the English-speaking market). He also gives us recommendations of singers and groups he likes. <strong>Interview is in English.</strong></p>
