		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://spanish-podcast.com/2007/12/06/vee-008-ritmo-latino-part-1/</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[Neil Hohmann, creator and producer of Ritmo Latino talks about the origins of this latino music podcast and the diversity of the music. This is the first part of a two-part interview with Neil. Part 2 will be podcast next week. Interview is in English.
Music featured in this episode:
Manu Chao
